Privacy Policy — TradeMatePro
Last updated: April 2026
1. Overview
TradeMatePro ("the App") is developed and published by G&V Maintenance Ltd. This privacy policy explains how the App handles your information.
2. Data collection
TradeMatePro does not collect, store, transmit, or share any personal data with G&V Maintenance Ltd or any third party. The App has no user accounts, no registration process, and no analytics tracking.
3. Data stored on your device
All information you enter into the App — including business details, customer names, estimates, quotes, and preferences — is stored locally on your device only, using your device's built-in storage (UserDefaults on macOS, localStorage on Windows). This data never leaves your device and is not accessible to anyone other than you.
4. Network access
The App connects to the internet solely to retrieve publicly available supplier pricing data to generate live price comparisons. No personal information, estimate data, or customer details are transmitted during this process.
5. Third-party services
The App does not use any third-party analytics, advertising networks, tracking services, or data brokers.
6. Children's privacy
The App is intended for use by tradespeople and businesses. It is not directed at children under the age of 13 and does not knowingly collect data from children.
7. Your rights
Since all data is stored locally on your device, you have full control over it at all times. You can delete all App data by uninstalling the App or clearing its local storage through your device settings.
8. Changes to this policy
If this policy changes in a future version of the App, the updated policy will be published at this URL and the "last updated" date will be revised.
